docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, June 15 A Chilean psychiatrist described today the use of LSD, along with other hallucinogens; in facilitating the mental transitions he desires for patients undergoing analysis.
docs.abstract: Dr Naranjo (Chile) uses LSD and other hallucinatory drugs for patients undergoing analysis
